    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Social Deduction &amp; Battle Royale</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819580/extras/efb21bd3c37417a48f1597e362a0aed5.poster.avif?t=1642697342\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819580/extras/efb21bd3c37417a48f1597e362a0aed5.webm?t=1642697342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819580/extras/efb21bd3c37417a48f1597e362a0aed5.mp4?t=1642697342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>One player starts as the <strong>illusionist</strong> and tries to kill everyone.<br></li><li>Others try to identify the illusionist.<br></li><li>If the illusionist dies, they leave an <i>orb</i> behind.<br></li><li>When a player takes the orb, they become the illusionist.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skills suited for assasination...</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819580/extras/55e20216a3b0cfa71bb86773239ca74b.poster.avif?t=1642697342\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819580/extras/55e20216a3b0cfa71bb86773239ca74b.webm?t=1642697342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819580/extras/55e20216a3b0cfa71bb86773239ca74b.mp4?t=1642697342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >...and mind games.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819580/extras/4574bb610be873182acac43926449bf7.poster.avif?t=1642697342\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819580/extras/4574bb610be873182acac43926449bf7.webm?t=1642697342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819580/extras/4574bb610be873182acac43926449bf7.mp4?t=1642697342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Positional Voice Chat</h2>You can only speak with players near you. Dead players can't speak.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No In-Game Purchases. No Progression.</h2>It's a simple game. Pick a name, customize your character, and join or create a lobby.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Top down camera<br></li><li>Right-click movement<br></li><li>Skills with cooldowns<br></li><li>Can unlock skills by collecting stars<br></li><li>Fast paced gameplay thanks to short rounds<br></li><li>Chat box communication for those not preferring voice</li></ul>",
